\line 6 \uc0\u1083 \uc0\u1077 \uc0\u1090 \uc0\u160 3 \uc0\u1084 \uc0\u1077 \uc0\u1089 \uc0\u1103 \uc0\u1094 \uc0\u1072 }\cell

